== Men who have sex with men (MSM) ==

Millett ''et al.'' (2007) found no association in three major US cities between circumcision and HIV infection among Latino and black men who have sex with men (MSM) . They conclude as follows: "In these cross-sectional data, there was no evidence that being circumcised was protective against HIV infection among black MSM or Latino MSM."<ref>{{cite journal
