}}
</ref>

Published meta-analyses, using data from the RCTs, have estimated the summary [[relative risk]] at 0.42 (95% [[confidence interval|CI]] 0.31-0.57),<ref name="weiss2008">{{cite journal
 |author=Weiss HA, Halperin D, Bailey RC, Hayes RJ, Schmid G, Hankins CA
